Marquesas Islands, Hiva Oa, trail toward Hanamenu; in gulch off trail, low forest, 3 August 1988 (fr). S. Perlman 10206 (AD!, BISH! [2 sheets], F!, K!, MO!, NY!, P [P00372510]!, PAP!, PTBG!, US!); Teakatu, valley on north side of Hanamenu trail heading down to Hanamenu past summit crest, between Teakatau and Tepuna, along stream bottom in 
